"color: rgb(0, 0, 187)">$name</span></font><font color="rgb(221, 0, 0)"><span style="color: rgb(221, 0, 0)">&quot;.&#160;I&#160;am&#160;printing&#160;some&#160;</span></font><font color="rgb(0, 0, 187)"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 187)">$foo</span></font><font color="rgb(0, 119, 0)"><span style="color: rgb(0, 119, 0)">-&gt;</span></font><font color="rgb(0, 0, 187)"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 187)">foo</span></font><font color="rgb(221, 0, 0)"><span style="color: rgb(221, 0, 0)">.<br />Now,&#160;I&#160;am&#160;printing&#160;some&#160;</span></font><font color="rgb(0, 119, 0)"><span style="color: rgb(0, 119, 0)">{</span></font><font color="rgb(0, 0, 187)"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 187)">$foo</span></font><font color="rgb(0, 119, 0)"><span style="color: rgb(0, 119, 0)">-&gt;</span></font><font color="rgb(0, 0, 187)"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 187)">bar</span></font><font color="rgb(0, 119, 0)"><span style="color: rgb(0, 119, 0)">[</span></font><font color="rgb(0, 0, 187)"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 187)">1</span></font><font color="rgb(0, 119, 0)"><span style="color: rgb(0, 119, 0)">]}</span></font><font color="rgb(221, 0, 0)"><span style="color: rgb(221, 0, 0)">.<br />This&#160;should&#160;print&#160;a&#160;capital&#160;'A':&#160;\x41<br /></span></font><font color="rgb(0, 119, 0)"><span style="color: rgb(0, 119, 0)">EOT;<br /></span></font><font color="rgb(0, 0, 187)"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 187)">?&gt;</span></font><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">&#160; </span></font></code>
